 an eventful third quarter</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912015114/image_912015114.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743082-bny-mellon-worldwide-growth-fund-inc-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 21:39:00"}, {"id": "4743081", "title": "Oversold Intel: Is A Rebound Likely?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Silicon Processor Chip\" data-id=\"1484082303\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FinkAvenue</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Since our last <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4733182-intel-stock-comeback-story-gains-momentum\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4733182-intel-stock-comeback-story-gains-momentum\" target=\"_blank\">analysis</a>, Intel (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) has dropped an additional 10%, extending its year-to-date decline to 56%. CEO Pat Gelsinger\u2019s planned exit has intensified market skepticism, raising doubts about the continuity of Intel\u2019s turnaround strategy, including its advanced node development</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743081-oversold-intel-is-a-rebound-likely", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 21:32:08"}, {"id": "4743080", "title": "Franco-Nevada: Five Reasons We Bought A Gold Position With A Yield", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176106891/image_2176106891.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Top view photo of vogue style trend grandfather lying christmas balls decor wearing glossy festive blazer\" data-id=\"2176106891\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176106891/image_2176106891.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176106891/image_2176106891.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176106891/image_2176106891.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176106891/image_2176106891.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176106891/image_2176106891.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176106891/image_2176106891.jp